column2: select p.stable_id ,      AGE.attr_value as AGE ,      DIAGNOSIS.attr_value as DIAGNOSIS ,      ETHNICITY.attr_value as ETHNICITY   from cancer_study cs    inner join patient p      on p.cancer_study_id=cs.cancer_study_id    left outer join clinical_patient DIAGNOSIS      on DIAGNOSIS.internal_id=p.internal_id     and DIAGNOSIS.attr_id =&&&    left outer join clinical_patient AGE      on AGE.internal_id=p.internal_id     and AGE.attr_id =&&&    left outer join clinical_patient ETHNICITY      on ETHNICITY.internal_id=p.internal_id     and ETHNICITY.attr_id =&&&  where cs.cancer_study_identifier=&&& order by #
